{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "第六回\"好亮的刀\"中，白玉京试图翻身逃跑却被方龙香再次制服。方龙香得意地揭露了全部阴谋：他杀了公孙静的老婆，青龙会通过孔雀图掌控天下最可怕的暗器孔雀翎的秘密。袁紫霞从公孙静手中盗走了孔雀图，公孙静假死躲藏却被青龙会识破。方龙香逼白玉京交出孔雀图，白玉京否认持有。方龙香搜查时发现长生剑剑柄中空，触发机关被藏在其中的牛芒毒针射杀。朱大少、苗烧天、赵一刀、白马张三等人闻声赶来，发现满屋死人，白玉京奄奄一息却还活着。赵一刀举刀砍向白玉京，留下悬念。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "想不到你点穴的手法又进步了些，可喜可贺。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "其实你根本用不着骗我回头，我也会让你试一次的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "你以为你刚才真的骗过了我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "若换了是我，也忍不住要回头去看看的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "但我却不必。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "因为我知道公孙静的老婆已死了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "你……你刚才已经杀了她？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "我不喜欢让活人留在我背后，虽然现在女人缺货，我也只好忍痛牺牲了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "我记得你以前好像是个很怜香惜玉的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "以前我也是个有两只手的人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "自从你只剩下一只手后，就不再信任女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "只信任一种，死的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "现在我们是不是可以接着继续谈下去了？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "谈什么？孔雀翎？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "据说天下的暗器一共有三百六十几种，但自从世上有暗器以来，孔雀翎无疑是其中最成功、最可怕的一种。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "我承认。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "最可怕的是，除了孔雀山庄的嫡系子孙外，世上从没有任何人能知道这种暗器的秘密，更没有人知道它是如何打造的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "的确没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "但现在却有了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "公孙静被人骗去的那张秘图，就是打造孔雀翎的图形，和使用孔雀翎的方法。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "这张图怎么会落在他手上的呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "青龙会若想得到一样东西，通常都有很多种法子的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "我知道青龙会一向对孔雀山庄很不满意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "但别人若也能打造孔雀翎，孔雀山庄的威风还能剩下来的就不多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "白马、赤发、快刀、万金堂，这些人好象都跟他们有很大的仇恨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "所以他们才会不惜倾家荡产，来抢购这张秘图。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "不错，江湖中肯不惜重价来买孔雀翎的人，一定还有很多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "也许比想买你的长生剑的人还多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "但青龙会为什么不自己打造这孔雀翎？为什么要卖给别人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "因为青龙会老大只对一样东西有兴趣。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "黄金。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "白银、珠宝也行。青龙会能得到这样东西，当然也花了本钱。青龙会开支可大得吓人，所以青龙老大才急着要将这东西脱手。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "而且这东西本就烫手得很，能早点甩出去，麻烦岂非就是别人的了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "对极了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "何况，江湖中拥有孔雀翎的人若是多了起来，死的人也就多了。你若用孔雀翎杀了他，他的家人想必免不了要弄个孔雀翎来复仇。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "那想必是一定免不了的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "这种事若是一天天多了起来，江湖中就难免要一天比一天乱。江湖越乱，青龙会混水摸鱼的机会就越多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "你们的青龙会老大真是个天才，连我都不能不佩服。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "想不到你居然是他的知己，我也佩服你。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "我手里若有了这么样一件东西，至少是决不会被人骗走的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "公孙静机智深沉，办事老练，本也是青龙会里的第一流好手，只可惜他也犯了个和你一样的毛病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "他也说谎？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "他好色，比你还好色。更不幸的是，他也跟你一样，他也是看上了那位袁姑娘。她实在是我见到的女人中，最懂得骗男人的。男人遇见她，不上吊只怕也要跳河。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "幸好我现在已用不着上吊，也用不着跳河了。我有个好朋友照顾我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "所以我说你运气一向不错。袁姑娘究竟是怎么样将这东西盗走的，现在我倒还是不大清楚。据我所猜想，她一定是趁着公孙静累极了的时候，将他的钥匙打成模子，另外做了一副，再买通了看守地道的人盗走的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "你们想得很合理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "她算准事发之后，公孙静一定也会赶快逃走；被她买通了的守卫，自己也脱不了罪，当然也不会将这件事泄露出来。这位袁姑娘的确算得很精，只可惜还是忘了一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "她忘了青龙会若要人说话，只怕连死人都会开口的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "是不是那守卫说出了她的行踪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "她买通了两个守卫，乘着换班的时候，混入秘道，用她自己复制的钥匙，盗走了孔雀图，再乘着换班时溜了出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "她为什么不将这两个守卫杀了灭口？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "因为她怕惊动别人，因为她武功不高明，何况那时她剩下的时间已不多。所以你若认为她的心还不够狠，你就错了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "我看人总是常常看错的，否则我怎会交到你这样的好朋友。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "青龙会耳目遍布天下，既然已知道她是这么样的一个人，当然就不会查不出她的行踪下落。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "公孙静当然也不甘心，也想将这东西要回来。但青龙会处置叛徒的法子，他也一向清楚得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "所以他才假装死人，躲在棺材里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "他以为这法子已经高明极了，安全极了，但他只怕永远也不会想到，他买棺材那家店，也是青龙会开的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "青龙会对自己兄弟照顾得倒真周到。你只要一进了青龙会，它就已将后事替你准备好了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "那至少总比死了被人抛去喂狗好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "那两个和尚呢？已经喂了狗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "那两人当然也是他的同党，临时扮成和尚混到这里来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "只可惜他们的头太光，衣服太新，而且眼睛太喜欢看大姑娘。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "就因为他们的行迹被看破，所以毒针才会将他们杀了灭口，却想嫁祸在苗烧天身上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "去翻箱子的人是谁呢？是不是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "这种事又何必我自己动手？别人把东西搜出来，岂非也一样是我的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "若不是你，就一定是张三或赵一刀，那时只有他们有机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "我只可惜你送去的那些好菜好酒。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "公孙静虽然沉得住气，但也怕夜长梦多，所以发现我们都在楼下时，就急着去找袁紫霞了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "我看着他上去的。他本来还想跟袁紫霞好好商量，谁知道这位小姐竟是软硬不吃，因为她知道只要一叫起来，你就会赶上去英雄救美的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "最好笑的是，我居然还将她交给了你，居然还要你去保护她。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "受人之托，忠人之事，我一定会将她保护得很好的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "现在你总已大功告成了，你还要什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "大功还没有告成，还差一点。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "孔雀图还在别人手里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "在谁手里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "在我手里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "你不承认？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "女人……唉，她自己明明叫我死也不要说出这秘密，谁知道她自己反而先说了出来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "我早已告诉过你，青龙会若要人说话，连死人都要开口，何况女人？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "你若要女人保守秘密，只怕比要死人开口还困难些。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "我也告诉过你，你还有两条路可走，第二条路保证比第一条路愉快多了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "第二条路怎么走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "带着你的孔雀图入青龙会，公孙静那一坛就让给你做坛主。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我笑我自己。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "笑你自己？为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "因为我几乎又要相信你的话了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "你不信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "其实你显然已知道孔雀图在我这里。既然有法子能要我开口，又何必说这种好听的话来骗我高兴？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "因为你是个人才，青龙会需要各种人才。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "但我还是不相信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "要怎么样你才相信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "你先放了我，我就将孔雀图交出来。决不骗你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "幸好你刚才提醒过我，否则几乎又要相信你的话了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "我也知道这交易是谈不成功的，但我也有件事要告诉你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "我若不想说话的时候，世上决没有任何人能要我开口。我若不说出孔雀图在哪里，世上决没有任何人找得到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "这一日一夜里，你根本没有到别的地方去过，我最多将这地方每一寸都翻过来，还怕找不到？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "要找，自然要从你身上找起。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "欢迎得很。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若是你，我会将那孔雀图藏在什么地方呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "你不是我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "不错，我不是你，我也没有你的长生剑。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "以后有机会，我一定会去换一个。",
      "tone": "勉强",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "用不着，我现在就可以替你换。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "speaker_name": "白玉京",
      "listener": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "text": "不必费神了，你的好意我心领了就是。",
      "tone": "勉强",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "大家既然是好朋友，又何必客气。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咦，这里面怎么好像是空的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_long_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "方龙香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯，果然是空的，——里面好像有卷纸。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方店主，你在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出了什么事？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你能断定刚才是方老板的声音？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "决不会错。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这间房却是那老太婆住的。",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早就觉得那老太婆有点鬼鬼祟祟的样子。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_zhang_san",
      "speaker_name": "白马张三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看见了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_shao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "苗烧天",
      "listener": "char_bai_ma_zhang_san",
      "text": "死人，一屋子死人。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
