    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_zhang_san",
      "speaker_name": "白马张三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然全都死了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_yi_dao",
      "speaker_name": "赵一刀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方店主怎么会跟这老……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_zhang_san",
      "speaker_name": "白马张三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人又是谁？……公孙静？怎么会是公孙静？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "朱大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位难道未看出这里还有个活的！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_yi_dao",
      "speaker_name": "赵一刀",
      "listener": "char_zhu_da_shao",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "朱大少",
      "listener": "char_zhao_yi_dao",
      "text": "当然是位死不了的人。",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "朱大少",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_jing",
      "text": "白公子睡着了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_zhang_san",
      "speaker_name": "白马张三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白玉京也在这里，他果然还没有死。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "朱大少",
      "listener": "char_bai_ma_zhang_san",
      "text": "莫忘记白公子是长生的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_zhang_san",
      "speaker_name": "白马张三",
      "listener": "char_zhao_yi_dao",
      "text": "却不知他的头疼不疼？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 480,
